Bert Bailey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bert_Bailey 0 Albert Edward Bailey (11 June 1868 – 30 March 1953), better known as Bert Bailey, was a New Zealand-born Australian writer, theatrical manager and actor best known for playing Dad Rudd on stage and screen.
